description:
Take a look at the latest featurette for Marvel Television’s Agatha All Along as viewers take a stroll down memory lane for the first MCU official series, WandaVision where Agatha's story began.

In Marvel Studios’ “Agatha All Along,” the infamous Agatha Harkness finds herself down and out of power after a suspicious goth Teen helps break her free from a distorted spell. Her interest is piqued when he begs her to take him on the legendary Witches’ Road, a magical gauntlet of trials that, if survived, rewards a witch with what they’re missing. Together, Agatha and this mysterious Teen pull together a desperate coven, and set off down, down, down The Road…

This Halloween season, stream Marvel Television’s Agatha All Along. The two-episode premiere arrives September 18 on ‪Disney+

#AgathaAllAlong #MCU #WandaVision
title: Agatha All Along - Official 'Rewinding WandaVision' Featurette (2024) Elizabeth Olsen, Kathryn Hahn

description:
Check out this Dead Rising Deluxe Remaster Chris Redfield DLC costume trailer. The Dead Rising Deluxe Remaster Resident Evil Hero Pack features the Chris Redfield costume and the Save Theme from Resident Evil 1 Remake. It's available in the Digital Deluxe edition of the game, and can also be purchased as a Costume & BGM pack.

Dead Rising Deluxe Remaster will be released digitally on September 19, 2024 for PS5 (PlayStation 5), Xbox Series X/S, and Steam (PC), with the physical version of the game available from November 8.

#DeadRising #ResidentEvil #Gaming
title: Dead Rising Deluxe Remaster - Official Chris Redfield DLC Costume Teaser Trailer

description:
Take a look at the Power Sword trailer for Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2, an upcoming third-person action shooter developed by Saber Interactive. Wield the Power Sword, a weapon that emits elegance and lethality. The Power Sword can also be switched into two different stances, one for speed and the other for broader attacks. Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 is launching on September 9 for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC.

#SpaceMarine2 #Warhammer #Gaming
title: Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 - Official Power Sword Trailer

description:
Check out the Street Fighter 6 Terry Arrives! Fighting Pass trailer, spotlighting what's in the latest Street Fighter fighting pass, out on September 2. Get a look at the new Fatal Fury-themed rewards, including avatar gear, music themes, new Challenger screen effects, stickers, and more. The Battle Hub will also be redesigned with a new SNK x Street Fighter 6 theme.

Terry Bogard arrives in Street Fighter 6 on September 24, 2024 for PS5 (PlayStation 5), Xbox Series X/S, PS4 (PlayStation 4), and PC (Steam).
